===Main drops===

The probability for a player to receive a [[runite ore]] drop depends on the player's mining level. The rock will deplete after receiving the Runite ore, unless affected by the effect of [[Superior mining gloves|superior]] or [[Expert mining gloves|expert mining gloves]].


{{DropsTableHead}}
{{DropsLineSkill|name=Runite ore|quantity=1|rarity=Always|skill=Mining}}
{{DropsTableBottom}}

The chance of successfully mining a runite rock varies from 11/256 at level 1 (if such a thing were possible), up to 19/256 at level 99.{{CiteTwitter|author=Mod Ash|url=https://twitter.com/JagexAsh/status/874241569091710976|quote=7.1% per roll at 99, 3.9% per roll at level 1 (assuming you were even allowed to try).|date=12 June 2017|archiveurl=https://archive.is/vODtT|archivedate=26 September 2020}}

